OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1778854269
OL,3,CMan caught on CCTV 'demonstrating' how
OL,4,Cto stab someone
OL,6,FA Scarborough man has been jailed for
OL,7,Fsix months within three days of being
OL,8,Fcaught on CCTV lunging at a man with a
OL,9,Fpair of scissors.
OL,11,FJerome Christian Clough, 30, of Prince
OL,12,Fof Wales Terrace, was seen on CCTV on
OL,13,Fthe morning of Saturday 9 May in what
OL,14,Fappeared to be a heated conversation
OL,15,Fwith two other people.
OL,17,FHe was then seen to take a pair of
OL,18,Fscissors from his pocket and lunge at
OL,19,Fthe man he was in conversation with.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
