OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,370,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1778854269
OL,3,CMan caught on CCTV 'demonstrating' how
OL,4,Cto stab someone
OL,6,FCCTV operators alerted North Yorkshire
OL,7,FPolice at 6.38am and Clough was
OL,8,Farrested two minutes later, despite
OL,9,Frunning off from the scene.
OL,11,FAlthough no complaint was received by
OL,12,Fthe victim, due to the CCTV officers
OL,13,Fwere able to charge Clough with
OL,14,Fpossessing a bladed article and affray.
OL,16,FHe appeared at York Magistrates' Court
OL,17,Fon 11 May where he pleaded guilty to
OL,18,Fboth offences and was jailed for 26
OL,19,Fweeks for affray and eight weeks for
OL,20,Fpossessing the blade.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,370,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1778854269
OL,3,CMan caught on CCTV 'demonstrating' how
OL,4,Cto stab someone
OL,6,FIn an interview with police, Clough
OL,7,Fclaimed he used the scissors for art
OL,8,Fand craft and that he was actually
OL,9,Fshowing the victim an example of how
OL,10,Fto stab someone that he had seen on a
OL,11,Fvideo.
OL,13,FInvestigating officer, Detective
OL,14,FConstable Alfie Thomlinson, said:
OL,15,F"Clough was seen in broad daylight -
OL,16,Fas the town was waking up and busy
OL,17,Fwith workers, residents and visitors -
OL,18,Fclearly lunging at a man with a pair
OL,19,Fof scissors.
OL,26,@wD@AOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,370,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1778854269
OL,3,CMan caught on CCTV 'demonstrating' how
OL,4,Cto stab someone
OL,6,F"The swift action of the CCTV
OL,7,Foperators followed by the immediate
OL,8,Fresponse of officers on the ground
OL,9,Fmeant he was detained within two
OL,10,Fminutes of the report coming in to us.
OL,12,F"By the following morning, he was
OL,13,Fcharged and remanded by detectives
OL,14,Fworking with the Crown Prosecution
OL,15,FService and by Monday morning he was
OL,16,Fsent to jail by Magistrates.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
