OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,370,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1778854269
OL,3,CMan caught on CCTV 'demonstrating' how
OL,4,Cto stab someone
OL,6,F"Clough denied that he did anything
OL,7,Fwrong in his police interview,
OL,8,Fclaiming his scissors were for art and
OL,9,Fcraft purposes and that he was merely
OL,10,Fdemonstrating something he had seen in
OL,11,Fa video.
OL,13,F"Hopefully he can now take time to
OL,14,Freflect on his behaviour and
OL,15,Funderstand how serious this violent
OL,16,Fact could have been if contact was
OL,17,Fmade with the man.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/6
