PN,36906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1778854269
OL,3,CMan caught on CCTV 'demonstrating' how
OL,4,Cto stab someone
OL,6,F"Violent behaviour involving blades
OL,7,Fwill simply not be tolerated on the
OL,8,Fstreets of North Yorkshire, and this
OL,9,Fshould be a clear message to anyone
OL,10,Fwho thinks about carrying any kind of
OL,11,Fweapon."
